#: _posts/2024-07-12-quarkus-newsletter-46.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Check out \"Crafting a Local RAG application with Quarkus\" by Clement "
"Escoffier to learn how to build an AI-infused chatbot application using "
"Quarkus, LangChain4j, Infinispan, and the Granite LLM. See how to create an "
"entirely local solution, eliminating the need for any cloud services, "
"including the LLM. Read Hantsy's \"Integrating Jakarta Data with Quarkus\" "
"to see how to utilize the existing Hibernate ORM extension to integrate "
"Jakarta Data with Quarkus. Don't miss \"Stateful and reactive stream "
"processing applications with Apache Kafka, Quarkus, and Angular on "
"OpenShift\" by Hans-Peter Grahsl and learn how to build an end-to-end "
"reactive stream processing application using Apache Kafka as an event "
"streaming platform, Quarkus for your backend, and a frontend written in "
"Angular.  In the end, you'll deploy all three containerized applications on "
"the Developer Sandbox for Red Hat OpenShift. \"4 ways to deploy Quarkus "
"applications in OpenShift Container Platform 4\" by Francisco De Melo Junior "
"and Alexander Barbosa Ayala describes the BuildConfig process for Quarkus "
"applications in Red Hat OpenShift Container Platform 4."
msgstr ""
"查看 Clement Escoffier 撰写的 \"使用 Quarkus 创建本地 RAG 应用程序\"，了解如何使用 "
"Quarkus、LangChain4j、Infinispan 和 Granite LLM "
"构建人工智能聊天机器人应用程序。了解如何创建一个完全本地化的解决方案，从而无需任何云服务，包括 LLM。阅读 Hantsy 的 \"将 Jakarta "
"Data 与 Quarkus 集成\"，了解如何利用现有的 Hibernate ORM 扩展将 Jakarta Data 与 Quarkus "
"集成。千万不要错过 Hans-Peter Grahsl 撰写的《在 OpenShift 上使用 Apache Kafka、Quarkus 和 "
"Angular 实现有状态和反应式流处理应用》，了解如何使用 Apache Kafka 作为事件流平台、Quarkus 作为后端以及 Angular "
"编写的前端来构建端到端的反应式流处理应用。最后，你将在 Red Hat OpenShift 的开发者沙盒上部署这三个容器化应用。Francisco De "
"Melo Junior 和 Alexander Barbosa Ayala 撰写的 \"在 OpenShift Container Platform 4 "
"中部署 Quarkus 应用程序的 4 种方法 \"介绍了在 Red Hat OpenShift Container Platform 4 中部署 "
"Quarkus 应用程序的 BuildConfig 流程。"

